nodes.text: A male slicer operated in the Cularin system. During the time of the Clone Wars, the slicer traveled to Artom Station with the Dark Jedi Garth Ezzar and hacked into the computer system of the Comet Broom Service, altering the company's navigational data and planting a Trojan programme into the system, to aide Ezzar in his plot to incriminate the Jedi Order as being involved in Comet Broom's Cometary Water Reclamation Project.
